🚨 𝐁𝐑𝐄𝐀𝐊𝐈𝐍𝐆: Manchester City 𝐚𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐞 personal terms with Rayan Cherki, official bid next! 💣

After signing Tijjani Reijnders, Man City prepare official proposal to Olympique Lyon for the deal to advance.

Agreement done on personal terms with the player who is next target at number 10… and then, Rayan Aït-Nouri as left back as part of Manchester City transfer plans.
